OL,3,CNI health chiefs tell Stormont of #50m
OL,4,Cbudget shortfall per trust for next
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe Chief Executives of Northern
OL,8,FIreland's five health trusts and the
OL,9,FNI Ambulance Service, have laid bare
OL,10,Fthe extent of the issues they face to
OL,11,FStormont's Health Committee.
OL,13,FThey painted a picture of a system
OL,14,Fthat has too little money, too few
OL,15,Fstaff, and is trying to see more and
OL,16,Fmore patients who are presenting with
OL,17,Fmore complicated illnesses.
