OL,3,CNI health chiefs tell Stormont of #50m
OL,4,Cbudget shortfall per trust for next
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FRoisin Coulter, chief executive South
OL,8,FEastern Health and Social Care Trust,
OL,9,Fopened by calling for "a radical
OL,10,Foverhaul".
OL,12,F"There are no quick fixes. What is
OL,13,Fneeded will take years," she said.
OL,15,F"Most of my chief executive colleagues
OL,16,Fand myself have spent over 30 years
OL,17,Fworking in health and social care in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and, genuinely, we
OL,19,Fhave never experienced anything like
OL,20,Fthis."
