OL,3,CNI health chiefs tell Stormont of #50m
OL,4,Cbudget shortfall per trust for next
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FNeil Guckian, Chief Executive of the
OL,8,FWestern Health and Social Care Trust
OL,9,Ftold the committee that each trust is
OL,10,Ffacing a #50million shortfall heading
OL,11,Finto the new financial year. He said
OL,12,Fthat for one organisation to make that
OL,13,Fsaving in one year, they'd have to
OL,14,Freduce staffing by 1,500, with the gap
OL,15,Ffilled by agency staff.
OL,17,FMichael Bloomfield of the NIAS Trust
OL,18,Fsaid the Ambulance Service lost
OL,19,F108,000 hours waiting to hand patients
OL,20,Fover at hospital in 2023.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/12
