OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FHe said: "Regrettably many patients
OL,8,Fare waiting too long for an ambulance
OL,9,Fresponse in the community.
OL,11,F"While we always prioritise the most
OL,12,Furgent calls, response times, even for
OL,13,Fthe most clinically urgent calls, are
OL,14,Fincreasing.
OL,16,F"Of particular concern is the increase
OL,17,Fin response times for category two
OL,18,Fcalls, which should receive an 18-
OL,19,Fminute response.
