OL,7,F"We had a mean of 34 minutes in
OL,8,Fquarter one of this (financial year),
OL,9,Fthat has increased to 57 minutes by
OL,10,Fquarter three.
OL,12,F"The main reason for this increase is
OL,13,Fthe impact of wider pressures across
OL,14,Fthe unscheduled care system."
