OL,7,FSpeaking of waiting lists, Bernie
OL,8,FOwens of Belfast Trust told the
OL,9,Fcommittee that across NI there are
OL,10,F116,000 people waiting for an
OL,11,Finpatient or day procedure, 190,000
OL,12,Fpeople waiting for a diagnostic test,
OL,13,Fand 430,000 waiting for a first
OL,14,Fconsultant led outpatient appointment.
