OL,7,FAs for issues filling some posts,
OL,8,FMaria O'Kane (Southern Trust) said
OL,9,Fsome areas have 50 per cent vacancies
OL,10,Fin consultant psychology and
OL,11,Fpsychiatry posts, while some areas
OL,12,Fshort of 50 per cent of social work
OL,13,Fstaff.
OL,15,FJennifer Welsh, chief executive of the
OL,16,FNorthern Health and Social Care Trust,
OL,17,Fbriefed MLAs on population challenges.
OL,19,FShe said 17.2% of the population is
OL,20,Fnow over the age of 65.
