OL,7,FShe added that healthcare is related
OL,8,Fto a number of social determinants,
OL,9,Fsaying almost half of preventable
OL,10,Fdeaths in Northern Ireland are
OL,11,Fattributable to deprivation.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the British Medical
OL,14,FAssociation has said that a 24 Junior
OL,15,FDoctor walkout planned from the 6th of
OL,16,FMarch will still go ahead, despite the
OL,17,FHealth Minister penning a letter
OL,18,Furging them to reconsider.
