OL,3,CNI health chiefs tell Stormont of #50m
OL,4,Cbudget shortfall per trust for next
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FMinister Swann had said he intends to
OL,8,Fincrease junior doctor pay in line
OL,9,Fwith the independent review body on
OL,10,FDoctors' and Dentists' pay. This would
OL,11,Fmean as much as 10.7 per cent for F1
OL,12,Fmedics.
OL,14,FDr Fiona Griffin, BMA NI junior
OL,15,Fdoctors committee chair said they have
OL,16,Fresponded to the Minister's letter.
OL,18,F"The current 'offer' is the DDRB's
OL,19,Fmost recent recommendation," she said.
