OL,3,CNI health chiefs tell Stormont of #50m
OL,4,Cbudget shortfall per trust for next
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"We have been consistently clear we
OL,8,Fare seeking an above inflation pay
OL,9,Frise for all junior doctors and a
OL,10,Fcommitment to working with us towards
OL,11,Ffull pay restoration.
OL,13,F"As it stands, what has been offered
OL,14,Fis not enough to avert strike action
OL,15,Fand our plans for this continue. We
OL,16,Fremain willing to work with the
OL,17,Fminister to agree an offer we believe
OL,18,Fis worth putting to our members."
