OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe letter from Minister Swann had
OL,8,Fsaid that while he understands and
OL,9,Fsympathises "with the frustration of
OL,10,Fjunior doctors", he would "question
OL,11,Fthe merit of the industrial action
OL,12,Fplanned."
OL,14,F"While I fully understand the anger of
OL,15,Fjunior doctors who have seen pay not
OL,16,Fkeep pace with inflation in recent
OL,17,Fyears, it is not realistic to expect
OL,18,Fthis issue to be resolved by the
OL,19,FExecutive and Assembly at this point
OL,20,Fin time," he said.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                         G11/12
