OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"Pay erosion has been a consequence of
OL,8,FUK Government fiscal policies over the
OL,9,Fpast decade and has been experienced
OL,10,Facross the UK public sector. This is a
OL,11,Fnational issue.
OL,13,F"I am committed to doing all I can to
OL,14,Fmatch awards given in England ` but
OL,15,Fparity plus for pay awards is not
OL,16,Fdeliverable."
